      "title": "9,000 Narcotic Pills seized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Alubomulla Police arrested two suspects who were transporting nearly 9,000 Narcotic Pills valued at over Rs. 1 Million in a van and a car in Hirana, Panadura on Sunday (4).",
        "Police investigations revealed that a card with 10 pills is sold for Rs. 1000/-,",
        "The suspects will be produced to the Panadura Magistrate's Court on Monday (5)."
      ],
